<strong>Steps to follow when drawing a graph;</strong>
<br>
<b>(i)</b>	First, create a table of values for the variables. <strong>Table of values</strong> is a table with corresponding values of variables.
<br>
<b>(ii)</b>	Identify ordered pair. <strong>Ordered pair</strong> means two numbers arranged in a specified order from a table of values e.g. the ordered pairs from the <strong>time-distance</strong> table below are;<strong> (0;0), (1;50), (2;100), (3;150),(4;200).</strong>
<br>
<table class="table table-bordered">
